# Group Emails
Welcome to the emails API. This API provides access to the emails service.

## emails [/emails]

### Create email [POST]

Create a new email

+ Request email (application/json; charset=utf-8)
    + Headers

            Accept: application/vnd.wantedly+json
    + Attributes

        + address: ADDRESS (string)
        + user_id: 1 (number)
        + user ()

+ Response 201 (application/json; charset=utf-8)
    + Attributes (emails, fixed)

### Get emails [GET]

Returns email list.

+ Request (application/json; charset=utf-8)
    + Headers

            Accept: application/vnd.wantedly+json

+ Response 200 (application/json; charset=utf-8)
    + Attributes (array, fixed)
        + (emails)

## email details [/emails/{id}]

+ Parameters
    + id: `1` (enum[string]) - The ID of the desired email.
        + Members
            + `1`
            + `2`
            + `3`

### Get email [GET]

Returns email.

+ Request (application/json; charset=utf-8)
    + Headers

            Accept: application/vnd.wantedly+json

+ Response 200 (application/json; charset=utf-8)
    + Attributes (emails, fixed)

### Update email [PUT]

Update email.

+ Request email (application/json; charset=utf-8)
    + Headers

            Accept: application/vnd.wantedly+json
    + Attributes

        + address: ADDRESS (string)
        + user_id: 1 (number)
        + user ()

+ Response 200 (application/json; charset=utf-8)
    + Attributes (emails, fixed)

### Delete email [DELETE]

Delete email.

+ Request (application/json; charset=utf-8)
    + Headers

            Accept: application/vnd.wantedly+json

+ Response 204

# Data Structures
## emails (object)

+ id: 1 (number)
+ address: ADDRESS (string)
+ user_id: 1 (number)
+ user ()
